<section data-grid="col-12">
        <h1 class="c-heading-2">FAQ</h1>
        <h2 class="c-heading-4">What opperating system does Surface Pro 4 run?</h2>
        <p class="c-paragraph-3">Surface Pro 4 runs full Windows 10 Pro. This means you can run your favorite programps, apps, and browsers.</p>
        <h2 class="c-heading-4">Can I run multiple programs at the same time?</h2>
        <p class="c-paragraph-3">The Surface Pro 4 lets you multitask like a pro. Run Windows apps and as many desktop programs as you need simultaneously - they will even snap into place on your screen so you can use them all at once.</p>
        <h2 class="c-heading-4">Does the Surface Pen that works with the Surface Pro 4 work with other Surface devices?</h2>
        <p class="c-paragraph-3">Yes. With Palm Block technology and 1024 levels of pressure sensitivity, Surface Pen gives you a surprisingly natural way to mark-up documents and take notes in your own handwriting.</p>
</section>

<section data-grid="col-12 pad-6x">
    <div data-grid="col-12">
        <h1 class="c-heading-3">You may also be interested in</h1>
    </div>

    {{#each product-detail.you-may-also-be-interested-in}}
        <div data-grid="col-3" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Product">
            <img src="{{this.image.src}}" alt="{{this.image.alt}}">
            <div class="x-type-center">
                <h2 class="c-heading-5" itemprop="name">{{this.heading}}</h2>
                {{> rating-template this.rating }}
                {{> price-template this.price }}
            </div>
        </div>
    {{/each}}
</section>

<section data-grid="col-12 pad-6x">
    <div data-grid="col-12">
        <h1 class="c-heading-3">The Microsoft difference</h1>
    </div>

    {{#each product-detail.the-microsoft-difference}}
        <div data-grid="col-3">
            <img src="{{this.image.src}}" alt="{{this.image.alt}}">
            <h2 class="c-heading-5">{{this.heading}}</h2>
            {{#if this.list}}
                <ul class="c-list">
                    {{#each this.list}}
                        <li>{{this}}</li>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
            {{/if}}
            {{#if this.paragraph}}
                <p class="c-paragraph">{{this.paragraph}}</p>
            {{/if}}
            {{#if this.call-to-action}}
                {{> call-to-action-template this.call-to-action }}
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    {{/each}}
</section>

<div class="m-v-md" data-grid="col-12">
    <hr class="c-divider">
</div>

<section data-grid="col-12">
    {{!-- TODO: Add offset --}}
    <div data-grid="col-3"></div>
    <div data-grid="col-6">
        {{#each product-detail.fine-print}}
            <p class="c-caption-1">{{this}}</p>
        {{/each}}
    </div>
</section>